Agility is the ability to respond to change rapidly based on changes to the market or environment, ensuring fast time to market.
Reference: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cloud-adoption-framework/strategy/business-outcomes/agility-outcomes

Option Elasticity  - Elasticity is the ability to automatically or dynamically increase or decrease resources as needed. 
Elastic resources match the current needs and resources are added or removed automatically to meet future needs when itâ€™s needed.
